## Quick Checklist

Before committing any component with colors:

- [ ] No hardcoded text colors (`text-slate-*`, `text-gray-*`, etc.)
- [ ] No hardcoded background colors (`bg-slate-*`, `bg-white`, etc.)
- [ ] Status indicators use `StatusBadge` or semantic status tokens
- [ ] User avatars use `UserAvatar` component
- [ ] Cards use `border` without color class
- [ ] Errors use `text-destructive` and `border-destructive`
- [ ] Brand colors used sparingly (CTAs, highlights only)
- [ ] Dark mode will work automatically (no manual dark: variants)
